32
00:01:23,514 --> 00:01:26,530
Mine says... "Swarley."

33
00:01:27,393 --> 00:01:29,526
How'd they get
"Swarley" from "Barney"?

34
00:01:29,542 --> 00:01:30,626
It's not even a name.

35
00:01:30,643 --> 00:01:32,736
