old Swarlz get that upset.

40
00:01:50,422 --> 00:01:52,922
Sync by vNaru

41
00:02:05,044 --> 00:02:06,589
Hey, guess what?

42
00:02:06,605 --> 00:02:07,527
Oh, sorry.

43
00:02:07,541 --> 00:02:08,568
